Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有发过这种邮件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.09,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,340)}香子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.09,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,408)}不要忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.09,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,472)}命中注定的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.09,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,544)}请联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.09,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,606)}我一直都在联系你
